{"tid":2446420,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"兩日41間工作場所上榜　兩間在IFC二期　H&M、CHANEL上榜","createTime":"2021-03-14T12:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T02:24:04.000Z","uid":159163,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee406eaae1e55d084d6ed6df6c7b8427224044b","tid":2446420,"uid":159163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T12:15:13.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情反彈，URSUS Fitness群組累計109宗確診個案，涉及多個行業。根據政府連續兩日(3月12、13日)公布的強制檢測通告，一共有41個工作場所上榜，當中涉及13間金融機構，佔近三分之一，包括位於國金二期的瑞銀集團、滙豐總行、中環渣打大廈。除了金融機構，強檢名單亦包括不少專業界別，包括4間律師事務所、多間顧問公司；更有為人熟知的時裝品牌辦公室，包括H&amp;M及Chanel。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210314/447811401629962240820793.png/iMpD8t-qskTwCeEWnuOM0XEk4UmMfRWJJgUAZSYFAGU?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210314%2F447811401629962240820793.png%2FiMpD8t-qskTwCeEWnuOM0XEk4UmMfRWJJgUAZSYFAGU%3Fv%3Dw640&h=3e8a3195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b0ac3e1e8fbf9e14b43ba0b8d81452b8c0ceff2","tid":2446420,"uid":301838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"點解h&amp;m咁多靚仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ef2093c80bc4c7d4b3334040409aefa5a02e0f","tid":2446420,"uid":159163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2b0ac3e1e8fbf9e14b43ba0b8d81452b8c0ceff2","tid":2446420,"uid":301838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"點解h&amp;m咁多靚仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}